  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale-data variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). NOTE: model turbulence closure coefficients were updated on 2025-09-15; the primary experimental dataset carries a dataVintage of 2025-08-22, predating that revision. The assessment team judged the revision 'not material' to dataset relevance without formal re-validation.",
