    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 requirements table. The primary experimental dataset (dataVintage 2025-08-22) predates the model turbulence-coefficient revision (2025-09-15) by approximately three weeks; the assessment team determined this revision was not material to the hemolysis-index predictions and did not require re-execution of validation runs. On the basis of the overall credibility evidence, the CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
